question: Which movies were released in 1995?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.release_date STARTS WITH '1995'
RETURN m.title, m.release_date
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: List the first 3 movies with a budget over 50 million.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.budget > 50000000
RETURN m.title, m.budget
ORDER BY m.budget DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has budget $b; sort $b desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "budget": $b };

question: What are the latest 3 movies added to the database?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.release_date
ORDER BY m.release_date DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: Which production companies have produced movies with a budget over 50 million?
cypher:
MATCH (c:ProductionCompany)-[:PRODUCED_BY]-(m:Movie)
WHERE m.budget > 50000000
RETURN DISTINCT c.name AS company
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, producer: $pc) isa produced_by; $pc has production_company_name $pcn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "company": $pcn };

question: What are the languages available for the movie 'Toy Story'?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie {title: 'Toy Story'})-[:SPOKEN_IN_LANGUAGE]->(l:Language)
RETURN l.name AS language
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, lang: $l) isa original_language; $l has language_name $ln; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "language": $ln };

question: Which movies have a homepage listed?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.homepage IS NOT NULL
RETURN m.title, m.homepage
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t };

question: List the first 5 movies sorted by popularity in descending order.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
RETURN m.title, m.popularity
ORDER BY m.popularity DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has popularity $p; sort $p desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "popularity": $p };

question: What are the original titles of movies that have been translated to Spanish?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:SPOKEN_IN_LANGUAGE]->(:Language {name: 'Spanish'})
WHERE m.original_language <> 'es'
RETURN m.original_title
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, lang: $l) isa original_language; $l has language_name $ln; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "language": $ln };

question: Who are the top 5 most frequent directors in the movies dataset?
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[r:CREW_FOR]->(m:Movie)
WHERE r.job = 'Director'
RETURN p.name AS director, count(m) AS num_movies
ORDER BY num_movies DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $p isa person, has person_name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (crew_member: $p, production: $m) isa crew_for; limit 5; fetch { "crew": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which countries have produced movies with a revenue exceeding 200 million?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:PRODUCED_IN_COUNTRY]->(c:Country)
WHERE m.revenue > 200000000
RETURN DISTINCT c.name AS country
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, location: $c) isa produced_in_country; $c has country_name $cn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "country": $cn };

question: List the first 3 production companies by the number of movies produced.

question: Which countries have produced more than 10 movies in the database?

question: What are the first 5 production companies by the number of genres they produce movies in?

question: List the first 5 movies with a poster path ending in '.jpg'.

question: What are the jobs of the first 3 crew members for the movie with the highest budget?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[r:CREW_FOR]-(p:Person)
WITH m, r, p
ORDER BY m.budget DESC
LIMIT 1
WITH m, collect({job: r.job, person: p}) AS crew
RETURN m.title AS movie, crew[0..2] AS crew_jobs
typeql: match $p isa person, has person_name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (crew_member: $p, production: $m) isa crew_for; limit 5; fetch { "crew": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which movies have been translated into more than three languages?
cypher:

WITH m, count(l) AS languageCount
WHERE languageCount > 3
RETURN m.title AS movie, languageCount AS translatedLanguages
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, lang: $l) isa original_language; $l has language_name $ln; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "language": $ln };

question: Which movies have the most number of keywords associated with them?

question: What are the first 3 movies with the highest budget to revenue ratio?

MATCH (m:Movie)-[:PRODUCED_BY]->(c:ProductionCompany)-[:PRODUCED_IN_COUNTRY]->(country:Country {name: 'France'})
RETURN m.title
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, producer: $pc) isa produced_by; $pc has production_company_name $pcn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "company": $pcn };

question: List the movies that have been rated exactly 5.0.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)<-[r:RATED]-(u:User)
WHERE r.rating = 5.0
RETURN m.title
typeql: match $u isa user; $m isa movie, has title $t; (reviewer: $u, item: $m) isa rated, has rating $r; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "rating": $r };

question: What are the movies directed by 'Christopher Nolan'?
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person {name: 'Christopher Nolan'})-[:CREW_FOR {job: 'Director'}]->(m:Movie)
RETURN m.title
typeql: match $p isa person, has person_name $pn; $m isa movie, has title $t; (crew_member: $p, production: $m) isa crew_for; limit 5; fetch { "crew": $pn, "movie": $t };

question: Which movies have a runtime longer than the average runtime of all movies?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WITH m, avg(m.runtime) AS avg_runtime
WHERE m.runtime > avg_runtime
RETURN m.title, m.runtime
ORDER BY m.runtime DESC
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has runtime $r; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "runtime": $r };

question: List the movies that have been produced in more than three countries.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:PRODUCED_IN_COUNTRY]->(c:Country)
WITH m, count(c) AS num_countries
WHERE num_countries > 3
RETURN m.title AS movie, num_countries
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, location: $c) isa produced_in_country; $c has country_name $cn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "country": $cn };

question: List all movies that have a revenue of zero but have been highly rated.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.revenue = 0 AND m.average_vote >= 7.0
RETURN m.title, m.average_vote, m.revenue
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has revenue $r; sort $r desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "revenue": $r };

question: Which movies have been associated with the keyword 'high school' and have an average vote above 6?

MATCH (m:Movie)-[:HAS_KEYWORD]->(k:Keyword {name: 'high school'})
WHERE m.average_vote > 6
RETURN m.title, m.average_vote
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, tag: $k) isa has_keyword; $k has keyword_name $kn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "keyword": $kn };

LIMIT 5

question: What are the top 5 movies with the most extended release dates range within a collection?
cypher:
MATCH (c:Collection)<-[:IN_COLLECTION]-(m:Movie)
WITH c, m
ORDER BY m.release_date
WITH c, collect(m) AS movies
WHERE size(movies) > 1
RETURN c.name AS collection,
       movies[0].title AS oldest_movie, movies[0].release_date AS oldest_release,
       last(movies).title AS newest_movie, last(movies).release_date AS newest_release,
       duration.between(date(movies[0].release_date), date(last(movies).release_date)).days AS days_between
ORDER BY days_between DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, series: $c) isa in_collection; $c has collection_name $cn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "collection": $cn };

question: List the first 3 adult films that have been produced in the 'United States of America'.
cypher:
MATCH (a:Adult)-[:PRODUCED_IN_COUNTRY]->(:Country {name: 'United States of America'})
RETURN a.title
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, location: $c) isa produced_in_country; $c has country_name $cn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "country": $cn };

question: Which 3 genres are most popular according to the popularity scores in movies?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)
RETURN g.name AS genre, avg(m.popularity) AS avg_popularity
ORDER BY avg_popularity DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, category: $g) isa in_genre; $g has genre_name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: Which movies have a status of 'Released' and a vote count of over 1000?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)
WHERE m.status = 'Released' AND m.vote_count > 1000
RETURN m.title, m.vote_count
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t, has average_vote $v; sort $v desc; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "vote": $v };

question: What are the top 5 languages used in the original language of adult films?
cypher:
MATCH (a:Adult)-[:ORIGINAL_LANGUAGE]->(l:Language)
RETURN l.name AS language, count(*) AS count
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, lang: $l) isa original_language; $l has language_name $ln; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "language": $ln };

question: List the first 3 movies that were produced by 'Pixar Animation Studios' and have a budget over $100 million.
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:PRODUCED_BY]->(c:ProductionCompany {name: 'Pixar Animation Studios'})
WHERE m.budget > 100000000
RETURN m.title, m.budget
ORDER BY m.budget DESC
LIMIT 3
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, producer: $pc) isa produced_by; $pc has production_company_name $pcn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "company": $pcn };

question: What are the top 5 most popular genres based on movie data?
cypher:
MATCH (m:Movie)-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)
RETURN g.name AS genre, count(*) AS movieCount
ORDER BY movieCount DESC
LIMIT 5
typeql: match $m isa movie, has title $t; (content: $m, category: $g) isa in_genre; $g has genre_name $gn; limit 5; fetch { "movie": $t, "genre": $gn };

question: List the first 3 adult films with a runtime longer than 60 minutes.

LIMIT 3

question: Which 3 movies have the highest number of spoken languages?

question: Who are the first 3 directors with movies in at least three different genres?
cypher:
MATCH (p:Person)-[:CREW_FOR {job: 'Director'}]->(m:Movie)
WITH p, count(distinct m.id) AS num_movies, collect(distinct m.id) AS movie_ids
WHERE num_movies >= 3
WITH p, num_movies, movie_ids
UNWIND movie_ids AS movie_id
MATCH (m:Movie {id: movie_id})-[:IN_GENRE]->(g:Genre)
WITH p, num_movies, collect(distinct g.name) AS genres

RETURN p.name AS director, num_movies, genres
ORDER BY num_movies DESC
LIMIT 3
